Install package (without virtualenv):
pip install -U scikit-image

Update pip3:
sudo -H pip3 install --upgrade pip

Can run code, but problem with Gtk3Agg Backend 
https://github.com/matplotlib/matplotlib/issues/2976

Install cffi:
sudo apt-get install python3-cffi

sudo pip3 install --upgrade cffi

Install cairocffi:
sudo pip3 install cairocffi




